                            "text": "<p>Nature provides everything we need, so we leave the rest out. We are committed to keeping our yerba mate completely free from artificial preservatives, hidden sugars, and synthetic fillers. From the first sip to the last, you are enjoying 100% plant-based purity.</p>",
